	&lt;li&gt;Indonesia is not a neighbour of India ( including the Andaman Nicobar Islands)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;India is a vast country. Lying entirely in the Northern hemisphere&amp;nbsp;the mainland extends between &lt;strong&gt;latitudes 8&amp;deg;4&amp;#39;N&lt;/strong&gt; and&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;37&amp;deg;6&amp;#39;N&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;longitudes 68&amp;deg;7&amp;#39;E and 97&amp;deg;25&amp;#39;E&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The landmass of India has an area of &lt;strong&gt;3.28 million square km&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;India&amp;rsquo;s total area accounts for about &lt;strong&gt;2.4 percent&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;of the total geographical area of the world.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;India shares its land boundaries with&lt;strong&gt; Pakistan&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Afghanistan&lt;/strong&gt; in the northwest, &lt;strong&gt;China&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;(Tibet)&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Nepal&lt;/strong&gt; and&lt;strong&gt; Bhutan&lt;/strong&gt; in the north and &lt;strong&gt;Myanmar&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Bangladesh&lt;/strong&gt; in the east.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Our southern neighbors across the sea consist of the two island countries, namely&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Sri Lanka&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;the Maldives&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
